            "item_1_title": "Return Eligibility",
            "item_1_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    To be accepted, items must be:\n  </strong>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    • Submitted via our returns portal within \n    <span style=\"font-weight:600;\">30 days of fulfillment</span> \n    \n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    • Received by us within \n    <span style=\"font-weight:600;\">7 days</span> \n    of submission\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    • Unworn, unwashed, unaltered, and in original condition, free from makeup, odours, deodorant marks, or damage\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    • Returned with all original tags attached\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Items that fail inspection will not be eligible for a refund or exchange.\n  </strong>\n\n</span>",
            "item_2_title": "Store Credit",
            "item_2_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    If you choose, or are issued, <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">store credit</strong> (for example, when an exchange item is unavailable or you prefer credit over a refund), the following applies:\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    • Store credit is applied to your customer account and can be used at checkout for any future purchase on the MARAME store, either online or via our Shopify-powered checkout.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    • Store credit is valid for <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">12 months</strong> from the date it is issued. After this period, any unused balance will expire and cannot be redeemed.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    • Store credit cannot be transferred and is valid for use only at <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">MARAME</strong>.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    • If you use part of your store credit during checkout and a balance remains, the remaining balance will continue to be available and will still expire <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">12 months</strong> from the original issue date.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    We encourage you to use your store credit within the <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">12-month period</strong> to avoid losing any unused balance.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
            "item_3_title": "Exchanges",
            "item_3_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Exchanges\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    We offer free exchanges for different sizes & colours, but you can also choose to change your product for a different product entirely. \n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Exchanges are only processed once your return has been received and approved at our warehouse. Unless you chose our Instant Exchange option, where we ship your new product before receiving your return. We just take an authorisation hold on your card until the original product is received in good order. \n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    All exchanges are free of charge. \n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n \n</span></span>",
            "item_4_title": "Refunds",
            "item_4_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Once your return is inspected and approved, we’ll process your refund to your original payment method.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Refunds are free of charge and you will be refunded the full amount you paid for the product you are returning. \n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n\n   <br>\n   What we refund:\n  \n  <br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    ✔ Full value of returned items\n  </span>\n  <br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    ✘ Original shipping fees (for all orders, including international)\n  </span>\n  <br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    ✘ Duties, taxes, or return postage for areas not covered by DPD\n  </span>\n  <br>\n\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Please allow up to \n    <span style=\"font-weight:600;\">10 working days</span> \n    for the refund to appear in your account.\n  </span>\n\n</span></span>",
            "item_5_title": "How to Start a Return",
            "item_5_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    All returns must be submitted through our \n    <a href=\"https://returnsportal.shop/marame.\" style=\"color:inherit; text-decoration:underline;\">\n      Returns Portal\n    </a>. \n    This ensures your return is logged, tracked, and processed smoothly.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Once submitted, you’ll be able to choose between the following return options:\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Paperless return (QR code)\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Show your QR code at any Royal Mail or DPD drop-off location, no printer required, making returns fast and convenient.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Print-at-home label\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Prefer to attach a label? Download and print your DPD return label at home.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Both options are completely free for supported regions.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
            "item_6_title": "Free Returns Service",
            "item_6_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Supported areas\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    We currently offer free Royal Mail & DPD returns for orders placed in the following locations:\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    • Mainland UK<br>\n    • Scotland<br>\n    • Wales\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Not supported by DPD\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    DPD does not currently support returns from the following locations:\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    • Northern Ireland<br>\n    • Isle of Wight<br>\n    • All international locations\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    If you are returning an item from one of these areas, you will need to send it back using your own courier. We do not charge any additional returns fees where return postage is your responsibility.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
            "item_7_title": "International & Non-DPD Returns",
            "item_7_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    • You will be presented with your cost for return postage when submitting your return. <br>\n    • We are not liable for lost or damaged parcels<br>\n    • Original shipping fees are non-refundable<br>\n\n</span></span>",
            "item_8_title": "Fair Use Policy",
            "item_8_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    To protect the sustainability of our returns and exchange services, MARAME operates a quantitative Fair Use Policy.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Fair use threshold\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    If a customer returns more than \n    <span style=\"font-weight:600;\">10 items</span> \n    within any rolling \n    <span style=\"font-weight:600;\">6-month period</span>, \n    we reserve the right to take one or more of the following actions:\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    • Decline future returns<br>\n    • Decline exchanges<br>\n    • Decline fulfilling future orders\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    This policy is in place to ensure fairness for all customers and to prevent excessive or abusive return behaviour. Any action taken under this policy is at our discretion.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
